Alliance rules:
- main things are decided by the council (lord + bannerlords) or alliance vote;
- new players should be approwed by one of the council members;
- minimal participation: 1 tablet invested or 1 item helped in the  alliance port in a week;  
- green card rule: player who makes best score in alliance event get a green card;
- yellow card rule: for breaking one of the rules you get yellow card, 2 yellow cards - kick off. 
Yellow card is valid for 1 month and cancelled by green card;
- inactive for 10 days - kicked out if not notified one of the council members.

Allies: POL,SUN
NAP: CAS, RO, RO1, HUN, SFP
special NAP: NBG - no massive attacks
